arcana (0.12.3-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add TTL-based pruning for stale agent listings and mailboxes
    (ARCANA_AGENT_TTL, ARCANA_MAILBOX_TTL, ARCANA_PRUNE_INTERVAL)
  * Services are never pruned (re-registered from code on startup)
  * Fix: messages to registered-but-offline agents no longer silently
    dropped after a snapshot restart (empty mailboxes are re-created
    for every restored listing)
  * /deliver now returns 404 for truly-unknown addresses instead of
    silently accepting the message

 -- trans <transfire@gmail.com>  Tue, 21 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000

